kpi_info.title: Call attempts that are registered in each clear code group
kpi_info.use: Call attempts (0...9999999) that are registered in each clear code group. The groups can be changed with the command TMH. The field is updated when the circuit is released. In combination categories the field is updated when the first released circuit is released.
